Package: rune
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ca-certificates
Description: Docker-compatible container runtime with TUI
 Rune is a Docker-like and Docker-compatible container service written in Rust.
 .
 Features:
  * Container lifecycle management (create, start, stop, remove)
  * Image building from Runefile or Dockerfile
  * Docker Compose compatibility
  * Docker Swarm compatibility
  * OCI-compatible container registry
  * Terminal User Interface (TUI)
  * Unix socket daemon (Docker API compatible)
  * Custom container runtime using Linux namespaces and cgroups
